    v2 = ((tmp - (v0 + 0.10 + tmp + 0.08)) / 0.12)

    v2 = wp.sin(0.07)
    tmp = ((0.56 + wp.cos(tmp + 0.13)) + ((tmp + 0.25 / v1 + 0.96) + 0.88))
